Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.00,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well my dearest Revy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did want to watch, eh? Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you did it. You really did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to see my sword that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:25.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can all make the march to Hell together!
