Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better chase me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That woman's amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have a chance\nto do it with her in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better prepare the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:51.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
