Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.68,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna give it to me or not? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jumbo, the game's up.
