Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, he might be with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm counting on you, partner.
