Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're shit out of luck. I pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:16.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one is getting out of here alive. Not a single one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hell's motel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:22.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Run as hard as you can, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the boogeyman will get ya!
