Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you! God damnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're probably dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you! How can you talk like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of following you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got time to bitch, find the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:10.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do? The plan's fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're turning tail? Fine!
