Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:36.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as you're still hopping around, you must have not met up with Jumbo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:42.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who cares? I've been waiting to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met a female gunman before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:50.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally got our chance. Sleep with me, Ms. Revy.
