Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:55.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see how it is. Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:59.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When this can hits the floor, it's the signal, miss kitty-cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.72,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten,
