Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:08.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to fight like a gunman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:27.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd fight a third-rate sack of shit like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're happy to die, that's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Jumbo finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking bitch, stop! Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sack of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, god damnit!
