Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.06,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Jumbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.47,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you your prom date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:11.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't no fun. You're in the fucking way, sword-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The miss isn't here any more. I shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're done here, right? Go home and cook some takoyaki or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:30.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A treacherous little dog like you wouldn't kill your own paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:32.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see how you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Draw in any fashion you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards! I'll kill you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy and Mr. Gin must be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stay here a little longer, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:54.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I found out that you were\nbeing dragged into this incident, our affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:04.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You mentioned that I was being dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Mr. Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the center of all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,you are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again. You are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:26.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Yukio, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:33.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,succeeded as the 14th Washimine Group deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:41.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, for all intents and purposes, I hold the highest rank within the Washimine Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:48.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't dragged into this. I am in the center of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,are my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You knew what kind of place this was and stepped forward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it! They're filled with evil and without a shred of decency!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This world, where people like that\nbetray and kill one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:38.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima, I'll ask you again. Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just watch you become dragged into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't just watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe Mr. Bando committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:06.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the group's momentum gone, tormented by our parent group,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,when it was necessary to stand up against a stronger power,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:15.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,what if you were the only one\nwho could save them from that plight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:23.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To renew the brotherhood, someone from the family had to be involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:25.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say it, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, it was just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:39.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how ridiculous the deal is,\nmaking it happen is the only way we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is how we keep order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then what happens to your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one wanted this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not Mr. Bando, not Mr. Gin, and not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They were all desperate to keep you away from the fighting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:59.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure that you didn't stand in this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:07.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been standing here sooner, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! The Kousa Council are to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are trying to bear this burden by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:24.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what we talked about at the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That people are like dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,People are like dice, a certain Frenchman said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You throw yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,in the direction of your own choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:41.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't forced into this. I threw myself into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I chose to do what I could\nfor my father and the people who loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! You didn't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:54.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't see that, you'll be forced to live\nwith a burden that you don't have to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are in the twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:04.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can say those things because\nyou're staying in the twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:09.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to come here! If I don't believe that I chose this, I wouldn't have the strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If someone's life, honor... If their future is counting on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,what can I do but fight for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:23.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like tonight. If I didn't believe that I had chosen this responsibility, there's no way I could've endured it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:35.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I believed him, until one night, when the cops\nbeat the shit out of me for something I didn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:42.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever turn these stories on me,\nyou stop being one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:46.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:47.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:55.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Against the experience she has endured tonight, I am powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:02.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no words to give this girl in front of me, who's stumbling towards your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am... I am where I'm standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My legs aren't standing anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, are you the devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For your death, this is a little easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's at your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:42.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happens, the painful and the terrible. I decided to carry it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:47.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that if it saves everyone's... Mr. Gin's life, then I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Yukio, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.56,Copy of Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okajima, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you try to make a stand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:02.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't honestly understand what you were talking about in the café,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I can say it clearly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:09.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why you submerged yourself in\nthe southeast Asian underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:14.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,your Japanese life... no, you may have been seeking something outside of your normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:18.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, you haven't chosen anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't returning to the normality of the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,yet you're not going deeper into the evil of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:28.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're just... hesitating between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it earlier, you wanted to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:39.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Save the Washimine Group, Mr. Gin, the members, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you don't actually want to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want to lose the normal life that you thought you threw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:56.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you just watch me die, then you lose the very last of your memories of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:19:01.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To choose is to lose something, to leave something behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:05.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to lose anything, even that which you've thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You still hang on to a piece of yearning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:12.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who could you possibly protect like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who could you possibly save like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Answer me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to live normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:32.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should be in the same place as you,\nnot desiring a life of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Yukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but be jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:02.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet, baby. You sliced the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you show that to me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be short tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you and the translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to waste that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:28.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you're unlucky, there will be a chance to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I pray we never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock still hasn't returned to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:54.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What could he be wasting his time on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:58.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as well. There's nothing for him to do for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:03.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The assault on the Washimine Group will begin at 0750.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:09.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy all confirmed headquarters, offices, and hideouts with two teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The attack team has already moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:17.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shall destroy all of the Washimine forces immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:23.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Teach these Japanese the etiquette of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:19.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:22.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't seek the same life as him.
